The target object for which this commentary is made. The target is the immediate parent of this comment. For a question, comment, or rating the target will be the topic of this conversation (a WorkspaceObject). For answer the target will be an S2clQuestion. It may not be NULL.
The top level root commentary object of this conversation. Will be NULL if this is a "root" comment. Otherwise it will be a "root" commentary object. It may be NULL.

The rating value for this object with allowed values dependent on the rating type selected. "Like" and "5-Star" are the base values. "Like" allows for On or Off behavior. "5-Star" allows for 0-5 integer rating. It may be NULL.

Text content for this comment. This field is the commentary's text including html tags. It may be NULL.

TcStandardType.description: DEPRECATED. SEE SUPPORT ANNOUNCEMENT AW5.1. This object is a specific S2clCommentary type which indicates it is an answer to a question. It enables users to reply with an answer to a question (S2clQuestion) posted on a WorkspaceObject. Answers are related to an S2clQuestion object. S2clAnswer object is used exclusively by Active Workspace Active Collaboration application.

DEPRECATED. SEE SUPPORT ANNOUNCEMENT AW5.1. S2clAutoSubscriptionPref contains preferences that control automatic subscription based on various events for a user. Events such as creation of comments or questions will trigger a subscription for notifications of future updates for a user. S2clAutoSubscriptionPref object is used exclusively by Active Workspace Active Collaboration application.

S2clCommentary is the base object for Active Collaboration objects. Commentary objects are used to comment, rate, ask and answer questions about a WorkspaceObject. S2clCommentary object is used exclusively by Active Workspace Active Collaboration application.

TcProperty.description: Holds attribute definition to be rendered in social tiles. It's a runtime property. It may be NULL.

TcStandardType.description: DEPRECATED. SEE SUPPORT ANNOUNCEMENT AW5.1. S2clEnvelope extends Envelope for Active Collaboration to allow for an untyped reference to be attached. These references could be people or commentary. S2clEnvelope object is used exclusively by Active Workspace Active Collaboration application.
S2clExperience object enables users to give feedback on their experience. It's a type of rating. S2clExperience object is used exclusively by Active Workspace Active Collaboration application.

DEPRECATED. SEE SUPPORT ANNOUNCEMENT AW5.1. The S2clNotification object is used to inform the user that a commentary action has been triggered on a WorkspaceObject based on a prior subscription request. The types of triggers could be new commentary, replies to questions, or ratings of the WorskspaceObject. S2clNotification object is used exclusively by Active Workspace Active Collaboration application.

DEPRECATED. SEE SUPPORT ANNOUNCEMENT AW5.1. S2clQuestion is a specialized comment that we want to track answers. All questions are the root of threaded commentary. S2clQuestion object is used exclusively by Active Workspace Active Collaboration application.

DEPRECATED. SEE SUPPORT ANNOUNCEMENT AW5.1. S2clScalarRating is used to rate an object on a scale of 1 to 5. This rating also allows for a textual description or justification. S2clScalarRating object is used exclusively by Active Workspace Active Collaboration application.

S2clSocialSummary is an Administrative object where the running totals of all commentary actions are kept for a WorkspaceObject. Commentary actions include creation of comments, questions, replies, and ratings. S2clSocialSummary object is used exclusively by Active Workspace Active Collaboration application.

DEPRECATED. SEE SUPPORT ANNOUNCEMENT AW5.1. A tag is a non-hierarchical keyword or term assigned to an object. Tags are used to help describe an object and allows for it to be found again by browsing or searching. S2clTag object is used exclusively by Active Workspace Active Collaboration application.

DEPRECATED. SEE SUPPORT ANNOUNCEMENT AW5.1. S2clTagPropogation object is used to define whether to propagate a tag from a primary object to a secondary object based on the relation found in this object. So if a tag is added to a reply the tag is propagated its parent question. Only tags which are in the white list may be propagated. S2clTagPropogation is used exclusively by Active Workspace Active Collaboration application.

DEPRECATED. SEE SUPPORT ANNOUNCEMENT AW5.1. S2clToggleRating is used to mark S2clCommentary (comments and answers) as helpful. Users may mark objects they find helpful in some way. S2clToggleRating object is used exclusively by Active Workspace Active Collaboration application.
